OL,3,CShoppers urged by Which? to consider
OL,4,Cprotections when using 'pay by bank'
OL,6,FShoppers are being urged to consider
OL,7,Fwhat protections they have when making
OL,8,Fpayments, with the rise in "pay by
OL,9,Fbank" as an option.
OL,11,FPay by bank allows people to quickly
OL,12,Fand securely pay money directly from
OL,13,Ftheir bank account without needing to
OL,14,Fenter the recipient's bank details or
OL,15,Fuse a card.
OL,17,FBut Which? raised concerns that people
OL,18,Fmay be unaware of a "protection gap"
OL,19,Fif something goes wrong with a
OL,20,Fpurchase.
