OL,3,CShoppers urged by Which? to consider
OL,4,Cprotections when using 'pay by bank'
OL,6,FWhich? said pay by bank is a
OL,7,F"potential game changer" for
OL,8,Fbusinesses as they can sidestep card
OL,9,Ftransaction fees and also benefit from
OL,10,Freceiving customer funds immediately.
OL,12,FThere is also appeal for consumers too
OL,13,Fas refunds can be processed instantly,
OL,14,Fand card details are not shared when
OL,15,Fmaking a transaction ` eliminating the
OL,16,Frisk of them being stolen or
OL,17,Fcompromised.
