OL,3,CShoppers urged by Which? to consider
OL,4,Cprotections when using 'pay by bank'
OL,6,FPeople do have general purchase rights
OL,7,Funder the Consumer Rights Act, meaning
OL,8,Fthat goods must be fit for purpose, as
OL,9,Fdescribed and of satisfactory quality.
OL,11,FBut Which? said these protections are
OL,12,Fnot always easy to enforce and in some
OL,13,Fcases may end up with people needing
OL,14,Fto go to a small claims court.
