OL,3,CShoppers urged by Which? to consider
OL,4,Cprotections when using 'pay by bank'
OL,6,FPeople may also face difficulties in
OL,7,Fthe event of a business going bust,
OL,8,Fparticularly if there is an issue with
OL,9,Fa future-dated purchase such as a
OL,10,Fflight, a festival, or a household big
OL,11,Fticket purchase such as a kitchen or a
OL,12,Fsofa, the consumer group said.
OL,14,FJenny Ross, Which? Money editor, said:
OL,15,F"Innovations like pay by bank present
OL,16,Fopportunities for businesses and
OL,17,Fconsumers alike, but they're not
OL,18,Fwithout risk, particularly as they
OL,19,Flack the rigorous purchase protections
OL,20,Fyou get when paying by card.
