OL,8,Fpayment company GoCardless, said:
OL,9,F"Open banking payments are good news
OL,10,Ffor British consumers: they offer bank-
OL,11,Fgrade security measures, instant
OL,12,Frefunds, reduced fraud risk and,
OL,13,Fcrucially, small businesses that use
OL,14,Fthem don't face the same high fees as
OL,15,Fthey do for card acceptance. Lower
OL,16,Fmerchant costs mean shoppers get
OL,17,Fcheaper prices ` a real win-win.
